Package com.flag4j.core

Interface MatrixMixin<T,​U,​V,​W,​Y,​X extends Number>

Type Parameters:
T - Matrix type.
U - Dense Matrix type.
V - Sparse Matrix type.
W - Complex Matrix type.
Y - Real Matrix type.
X - Matrix entry type.
All Superinterfaces:
MatrixComparisonsMixin<T>, MatrixManipulationsMixin<T,​X>, MatrixOperationsMixin<T,​U,​V,​W,​Y,​X>, MatrixPropertiesMixin
All Known Implementing Classes:
CMatrix, Matrix, SparseCMatrix, SparseMatrix
public interface MatrixMixin<T,​U,​V,​W,​Y,​X extends Number> extends MatrixPropertiesMixin, MatrixComparisonsMixin<T>, MatrixManipulationsMixin<T,​X>, MatrixOperationsMixin<T,​U,​V,​W,​Y,​X>
This interface specified methods which all matrices should implement.
